advancedBacklinks-desc: MediaWiki extension for advanced backlink tracking.
advancedBacklinks-wikitext-only-tooltip: Show only pages linking here directly from wikitext, ignoring templates
advancedBacklinks-nowikitextlinkshere-ns: No pages link directly to $2 in the chosen namespace.
advancedBacklinks-linksheredirectly: The following pages link directly to $2:
advancedBacklinks-lonelypagestext: The following pages are not directly linked from or transcluded into other pages in {{SITENAME}}.
wikitextcontentlonelypages: Orphaned pages by direct links from pages in content namespaces
advancedBacklinks-contentlonelypagestext: The following pages are not directly linked from or transcluded into other pages in content namespaces in {{SITENAME}}.
advancedBacklinks-pref-change-link: Link to Special:AdvancedBacklinks in the sidebar instead of Special:WhatLinksHere
apihelp-query+ab_linkshere-summary: Find all pages that link to the given pages with through-transclusion information.
apihelp-query+ab_linkshere-param-namespa: Only include pages in these namespaces:
apihelp-query+ab_linkshere-param-show:
Show only items that meet these criteria:
;redirect:Only show redirects.
;!redirect:Only show non-redirects.
;direct:Only show direct (wikitext) links.
;!direct:Only show indirect links.
apihelp-query+ab_fileusage-summary: Find all pages that use the given files with through-transclusion information.
apihelp-query+ab_fileusage-param-namespa: Only include pages in these namespaces:
apihelp-query+ab_fileusage-param-show:
Show only items that meet these criteria:
;redirect:Only show redirects.
;!redirect:Only show non-redirects.
;direct:Only show direct (wikitext) links.
;!direct:Only show indirect links.
apihelp-query+ab_linkstats-summary: Show incoming/outgoing link statistics for a page
apihelp-query+ab_linkstats-param-through: Count links through redirects (true by default)
abusefilter-edit-builder-vars-back-templ: Number of pages that transclude this page
